      <title>由于石油现金增加了加拿大省的盈余，标准普尔上调了艾伯塔省评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/alberta-upgraded-by-s-p-as-gusher-of-oil-cash-boosts-surplus</link>
